<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.5.10">
<l>kārār puyalkaik kalikaṉṟimaṅ kaiyarkōṉ,</l>
<l>pērāḷaṉ neñcil piriyā tiṭaṅkoṇṭa</l>
<l>cīrāḷā centā maraikkaṇṇā taṇṭuḻāyt</l>
<l>tārāḷā koṭṭāycap pāṇi</l>
<l rend="indent">taṭamārvā koṭṭāycap pāṇi.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Treasure who, never leaving, took [his] place in the heart</l>
<l>Of the noble, the king of those of Maṅkai,</l>
<l>Kalikaṉṟi with hands [like] a rain-filled cloud,</l>
<l>You with bright lotus eyes, ruler with cool tulasī garland, clap your hands;</l>
<l rend="indent">broad-chested [lord], clap your hands!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
